---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Socials from '../../components/Socials.astro';
---
<Base title="Главная" lang="ru">
  <style>
    .hero { padding: 6rem 0 4rem; }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: #888;
      max-width: 480px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .cta {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      background: #f0f0f0;
      color: #0a0a0a;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .cta:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
  </style>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>bossto</h1>
    <p>Мысли, опыт и инструменты для тех, кто строит своё.</p>
    <a href="/ru/blog/" class="cta">Читать блог</a>
    <Socials lang="ru" />
  </section>
</Base>
